data.description: Beautiful Country Estate on 1+ acres with 3 seperate living units. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is freshly painted in and out with beautiful new hardwood laminate floors, plush new carpet, new custom cabinets, deluxe new granite counters, has new energy efficient windows, new water well and new roof. Has additional 1 bed, 1 bath unit and a studio with a bathroom and kitchen.
